  "The bulk of Nathan \"Natie\" Kirsh's fortune comes from Jetro Holdings, which owns restaurant supply stores Jetro Cash and Carry and Restaurant Depot.",
  "Kirsh owns 70% of the company, which supplies wholesale goods to bodegas, small stores and restaurants.",
  "Kirsh made his first fortune in his native Swaziland, where he launched a corn milling business in 1958.",
  "He expanded into wholesale food distribution in apartheid South Africa, and then into supermarkets and commercial property development."
